# git-ai-commit

**AI-Powered Conventional Commit Message Generator**

[![PyPI Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/git-ai-commit)](https://pypi.org/project/git-ai-commit/)
[![Python Versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/git-ai-commit)](https://pypi.org/project/git-ai-commit/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/yourusername/git-ai-commit)](https://github.com/yourusername/git-ai-commit/blob/main/LICENSE)
[![Build Status](https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/yourusername/git-ai-commit/test.yml?branch=main)](https://github.com/yourusername/git-ai-commit/actions)

`git-ai-commit` (or `gac`) is a CLI tool that analyzes your staged git changes and uses AI to generate meaningful conventional commit messages. No more struggling with commit message writers block вЂ” let AI do the thinking for you while you stay in control.

